    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/vad-cou2-compound01",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment is formally accepted as complete for submission purposes. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated. Seven factors were assessed and all show achieved levels below required levels at MRL 5. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps. The hemolysis NIH prediction shows 25–40% under-prediction at high-shear operating points. Monte Carlo UQ was not completed. The overall credibility is insufficient for regulatory acceptance of the VAD hemolysis claim; however, the assessment package itself is accepted as the definitive record of credibility status for COU2.",
